data.description: Come take a look at this stunning 3 bed 2 bath single level home. The yard has mature trees and fenced in back yard. 2 car attached garage with storage space.  Walk into a spacious great room with vaulted ceilings. Beautiful kitchen with hickory cabinets and lots of cabinet space. Large living room with energy efficient Z style pellet stove. Good sized bedrooms with master bedroom, bosting a walk-in closet and walk-in shower in the master bathroom. Have no more power bills with this complete on grid solar setup that runs the entire home. Sellers get a power credit most of the time and system is paid off. Contact listing agent for more info and to schedule your showings
